node.text: Hey pals!! #ad Today’s post is dedicated to the most recent anime I started, Fena: Pirate Princess It’s basically about an orphan girl Fena who escapes to an island of samurai-pirates and discovers the truth about her identity, then she tries to unlock her family secrets (and treasure). She becomes captain of a crew and they go on a bunch of cool adventures! I really love the mystery and romance in this one I’ve seen the first couple episodes and can’t wait to watch more! It’s also a Crunchyroll and Adult Swim original which is hella cool tbh :D Give this anime a watch on @crunchyroll if you’re looking for something new to watch I’m enjoying it a lot! #anime #crunchyroll #fena
